{"tid":2303303,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［美國大選］［簡單翻譯］有人整咗infographics講關於Sidney Powell對Georgia佐治亞州嘅指控","createTime":"2020-11-27T21:35:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-28T16:52:21.000Z","uid":308915,"like":83,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"9266e2fd3c832a40084f0ace9b6e334b11a9662e","tid":2303303,"uid":308915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T21:35:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://directorblue.blogspot.com/2020/11/infographic-shocking-allegations-of.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdirectorblue.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F11%2Finfographic-shocking-allegations-of.html%3Fm%3D1&d=xEw7bVcEuEkne8wYN5Y7ChURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=b3cb0a55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://directorblue.blogspot.com/2020/11/infographic-shocking-allegations-of.html?m=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">INFOGRAPHIC: The Shocking Allegations of Mass Vote Fraud Made by Sidney Powell in Georgia</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n喺美國大選相關嘅討論post見到有人貼咗上面條link出嚟<br />\n心思思諗住約略咁譯咗佢 一次過睇晒關於GA嘅情況<br />\n<br />\n成件事主要有三點指控：<br />\n1. 違反正常應有嘅選舉程序<br />\n- 冇保管好啲計票器材+一大堆選票<br />\n- 監票員被趕離場同被威嚇<br />\n- <strong><span class=\"x-large\">前所未有地</span></strong>「暫停」點票<br />\n<br />\n2. 唔安全嘅voting machines<br />\n- 個設計容許操作員可以<strong><span class=\"x-large\">容易地調動</span></strong>候選人啲票<br />\n- Audit logs 唔完整+唔安全<br />\n- 與<strong><span class=\"x-large\">外國勢力</span></strong>有聯繫<br />\n<br />\n3. 非法選票<br />\n- 冇核對簽名<br />\n- 冇對barcode或者驗證選票<br />\n- 點票過程較後段出現<strong><span class=\"x-large\">統計學上唔可能發生</span></strong>嘅情況（95%以上嘅票都係投同一個人，即係拜登）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SajU7Yp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSajU7Yp.jpg&h=eeb353b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n1.1 違反選舉程序：點票機+一堆選票未被妥善處理<br />\n<br />\n本身應該係喺選舉日前個星期五收到處理選票嘅相關機器同裝置，然後喺星期日喺信上簽署表示已經收到並密封（sealed）有關器材<br />\n<br />\n但喺今次，負責嘅職員表示佢哋被要求照舊喺星期日簽署信件表明已經收到，但啲機係直到選舉日嘅凌晨兩點鐘先到貨<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PPvQGnW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPPvQGnW.jpg&h=be5cd2f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.2 違反選舉程序：民主黨佔多數嘅郡（Counties）非法地阻礙共和黨監票員監察點票過程<br />\n<br />\n當喺審核（audit）或重點（recount）選票時<br />\n有人目擊Trump嘅票被計算成拜登嘅票<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O52PcuK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO52PcuK.jpg&h=2c7a3b0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.3 違反選舉程序：大量原始、一樣嘅選票（98%係投拜登）<br />\n<br />\n證人表示喺佢20年嚟處理選票嘅經驗中 佢發覺啲選票上對相關候選人嘅markings係<strong><span class=\"x-large\">異常地一致</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JFak3Ha.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJFak3Ha.jpg&h=e195dede&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n2.1 唔安全嘅voting machines：（至少）有96600張<strong><span class=\"x-large\">並非由合法選民所投嘅</span></strong>郵寄選票遭非法計入<br />\n<br />\n專家表示有成千上萬（hundreds of thousands）投川普總統嘅票被轉移（transferred）到前副總統拜登<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MLmsJPQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMLmsJPQ.jpg&h=37b16771&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.2 唔安全嘅voting machines：喺Floyd County被發現有隻USB到有從未被計過嘅3300張票；未清楚究竟重發生過幾多次<br />\n<br />\nDominion系統嘅中央累加器（central accumulator）並冇一個受保護、實時嘅audit log去記錄清楚各場重要選舉活動嘅日期同時間⋯⋯<strong><span class=\"x-large\">容許咗未經授權嘅用戶去任意地（arbitrarily）增加、更改或刪除log entries</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CVwkjn4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCVwkjn4.jpg&h=b1cd6451&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n3.1 非法選票：民主黨佔多數嘅郡（Counties）幾乎冇核對過簽名+容許大量投畀拜登嘅非法選票<br />\n<br />\n簽名被彈返轉頭嘅比率喺最近期嘅選舉中只有0.15%<br />\n不在席投票嘅更只有0.00167%，成個州嚟計只有30人<br />\n除咗Hancock County同Fulton County外，冇其他屬於都會區嘅郡有將任何一張不在席投票嘅選票彈過返轉頭，即使個簽名唔match都好<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D2wo1Fd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD2wo1Fd.jpg&h=8768a319&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.2 非法選票：有幾百位證人目擊到選票遭非法處理，即使被限制觀看點票<br />\n<br />\n有證人表示見到有兩個點票人員將Trump啲票擺落拜登嗰邊，再疊喺張檯，寫落張點票紙到<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OFQttnP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOFQttnP.jpg&h=88fb02a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n總結：<br />\n2020年11月3號所舉行嘅總統同國會選舉結果必須被擱置（must be set aside）<br />\n個結果已經係有違反憲法嘅嫌疑<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JDCLvEs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJDCLvEs.jpg&h=6d26a943&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9771e68b7f6bde752e2cbf4178979a5d22c4a207","tid":2303303,"uid":79117,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T21:39:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2cce143e8c77ad157e3c6aaada2e24d999ec826e","tid":2303303,"uid":135400,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T21:43:32.000Z","msg":"半夜幫推，翻譯辛苦了<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edeec770f0bd0971f0f500ef916e07164fd351c6","tid":2303303,"uid":135400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T21:43:46.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b2311e8a19462b38525ebb367001b465e9e3add","tid":2303303,"uid":135400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T21:44:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef41fb07012ad55aefcd0bc4972afef00cc3c0ed",